00:20:01,416 --> 00:20:03,208
...a girl.

486
00:20:03,708 --> 00:20:05,583
Oh well!

487
00:20:07,666 --> 00:20:10,291
I won't be able to enforce
discipline, now will I?

488
00:20:10,375 --> 00:20:12,416
Not if I'm worried
about that stuff!

489
00:20:12,500 --> 00:20:13,541
[MAWARI] Go out
and get 'em again

490
00:20:13,625 --> 00:20:16,333
tomorrow, Mawari Zenigata!

491
00:20:19,250 --> 00:20:24,208
♪

492
00:21:48,958 --> 00:21:51,375
[WALLA: VOICES] Masa today!

493
00:22:02,541 --> 00:22:03,500
[door opens]

494
00:22:03,583 --> 00:22:05,375
[PROPRIETRESS]
Hello, and welcome.

495
00:22:08,833 --> 00:22:12,000
[MASA] So then, you
decided to come after all.

496
00:22:12,083 --> 00:22:15,208
I didn't expect to
see you here today.

497
00:22:15,291 --> 00:22:18,375
[MASA] Are you sure
you're well enough?

498
00:22:18,458 --> 00:22:20,083
[MASA] In your
condition, drinking too

499
00:22:20,166 --> 00:22:21,750
much could aggravate
your injuries.

500
00:22:21,833 --> 00:22:23,625
Make things worse.

501
00:22:23,708 --> 00:22:25,541
[MASA] Owner. Let's have
something nice and

502
00:22:25,625 --> 00:22:27,291
light over here
if you don't mind.

503
00:22:27,375 --> 00:22:28,875
Sure.

504
00:22:29,791 --> 00:22:31,666
[MASA] Ah, yes.
The Bloody Tear.

505
00:22:31,750 --> 00:22:33,750
It's a house specialty.

506
00:22:33,833 --> 00:22:36,458
[MASA] This should be
just right for you today.

507
00:22:38,291 --> 00:22:39,666
[MASA] From what I'm told.

508
00:22:39,750 --> 00:22:43,791
You got those injuries when
you exited a moving train?

509
00:22:43,875 --> 00:22:45,625
[MASA] Quite reckless of you.

510
00:22:48,500 --> 00:22:51,750
[MASA] Perhaps you
did it for love?

511
00:22:51,833 --> 00:22:53,666
I do understand
how you feel,

512
00:22:53,750 --> 00:22:55,541
but sometimes life
is more pleasant

513
00:22:55,625 --> 00:22:59,250
when you do
things in moderation.

514
00:23:01,625 --> 00:23:03,916
Do ya not remember
who you're talkin' to?

515
00:23:04,000 --> 00:23:06,916
Ya might want to be
a bit more careful Masa.

516
00:23:07,000 --> 00:23:08,750
[MASA] Yes! Of course,
sir. I'm sorry, Boss!

517
00:23:08,833 --> 00:23:11,208
Unless ya wanna lose
some of those fingertips.

518
00:23:11,291 --> 00:23:12,458
[MASA] No no no... Please!
Please forgive me!

519
00:23:12,541 --> 00:23:15,166
When I start drinking,
I lose control.

520
00:23:15,250 --> 00:23:16,666
I'll have ya know.

521
00:23:16,750 --> 00:23:19,375
If my dear, darling little Sun
hadn't been on that train,

522
00:23:19,458 --> 00:23:22,375
I coulda stopped it with one
hand tied behind my back!

523
00:23:22,458 --> 00:23:23,375
And it woulda been easy!

524
00:23:23,458 --> 00:23:25,458
[MASA] Boss, please calm down.

525
00:23:25,541 --> 00:23:28,875
[MASA] If you thrash
around too much--!

526
00:23:28,958 --> 00:23:32,958
[MASA] Uh, Boss.
Boss, are you all right?

527
00:23:33,041 --> 00:23:34,250
Boss!

528
00:23:35,791 --> 00:23:36,500
[NAGASUMI] My grand summer
adventure is coming to a close.

529
00:23:36,583 --> 00:23:37,625
It's second term already!

530
00:23:37,708 --> 00:23:39,041
Sun sure looks great
in that uniform,

531
00:23:39,125 --> 00:23:40,583
though really, she'd
look good in anything.

532
00:23:40,666 --> 00:23:42,625
The whole class is swooning,
but, hey, she's my wife!

533
00:23:42,708 --> 00:23:44,125
Maybe I shouldn't say
that too loud, though.

534
00:23:44,208 --> 00:23:46,333
Anyhow, here's hoping that
school life is as fun as summer!

535
00:23:46,416 --> 00:23:48,916
Though that's probably
too much to ask.

